OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FPolling stations have now closed
OL,7,Facross the West Midlands as many
OL,8,Fcouncils in the region have been
OL,9,Fholding local elections.
OL,11,FCandidates from all parties in
OL,12,FBirmingham, Coventry, Solihull,
OL,13,FWalsall, Newcastle Under Lyme,
OL,14,FWolverhampton, Sandwell, Tamworth,
OL,15,FCannock Chase, Redditch and Dudley
OL,16,Fhave all been vying for votes and
OL,17,Fcampaigning for crosses on each of
OL,18,Ftheir respective area's ballot papers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
