OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FThe elections began at 7am this
OL,7,Fmorning, with voting concluding at
OL,8,F10pm tonight and the people have now
OL,9,Fhad their say on who they want to
OL,10,Frepresent them on their respective
OL,11,Fcouncil.
OL,13,FMost of the authorities will start
OL,14,Fverifying and counting the votes on
OL,15,FFriday, May 8 - apart from Dudley,
OL,16,Fwhich is happening tonight.
OL,18,FThe end of the Labour Tory dominance:
OL,19,FHow could the West Midlands change
OL,20,Fafter the 7th May?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
