OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FCounting will be taking place
OL,7,Fthroughout the night, with results
OL,8,Fexpected in the early hours of Friday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FHere at ITV News Central we will be
OL,12,Fbringing you the live updates
OL,13,Fthroughout the night as the results
OL,14,Ffor each of the wards in Dudley are
OL,15,Fcalled.
OL,17,FAs things stand
OL,19,FThe Conservatives currently have
OL,20,Fminority control in Dudley.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
