OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FNormally it's a straight fight between
OL,7,Fthe Tories and Labour, but this time
OL,8,Fall parties will be fielding
OL,9,Fcandidates including the Green Party,
OL,10,Fthe Liberal Democrats, Reform UK, the
OL,11,FBlack Country Party and a clutch of
OL,12,FIndependents.
OL,14,FFor this local election a third of the
OL,15,Fcouncil is up for grabs, with 25 seats
OL,16,Fbeing contested by 134 candidates.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
