OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FOf the seats being contested, eight
OL,7,Fcurrently belong to the Tories, Labour
OL,8,Fcurrently have nine, The Black Country
OL,9,FParty have three and Reform UK have
OL,10,Ftwo.
OL,12,FThere is one Independent seat and also
OL,13,Fone seat currently belongs to the
OL,14,FLiberal Democrats. One final seat
OL,15,Fremains vacant after Labour MP for
OL,16,FStourbridge Cat Eccles stood down from
OL,17,Fthe council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
