OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FAcross all 72 seats that make up the
OL,7,Fwhole of Dudley Council: Conservatives
OL,8,Fcurrently have 33 seats, Labour have
OL,9,F24, The Black Country Party have six,
OL,10,Fthe Liberal Democrats have five,
OL,11,FReform UK have three, with one
OL,12,FIndependent.
OL,14,FHow is Dudley shaping up?
OL,16,FReform UK is likely to do very well in
OL,17,FDudley. Most polling across the West
OL,18,FMidlands shows a mixed picture, with
OL,19,Fno party clearly in front. That's not
OL,20,Ftrue in Dudley.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
