CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778220032
OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FReform UK have a 21-point poll lead
OL,7,F(41%) on the next most popular party,
OL,8,FLabour (20%).
OL,10,FThis would be bad news for the
OL,11,FConservatives, who are currently
OL,12,Frunning the show, but only a third of
OL,13,Fcouncillors are put up for election.
OL,14,FEven if all of the seats up for grabs
OL,15,Fgo to Reform, they still wouldn't have
OL,16,Fenough for a majority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
