OL,3,CLive updates as votes are counted in
OL,4,CDudley for Local Elections 2026
OL,6,FThe Tory leader, Kemi Badenoch, has
OL,7,Ftold ITV News Central that she's open
OL,8,Fto working with Reform at the local
OL,9,Flevel, so there is every chance this
OL,10,Fcould be one of the country's first
OL,11,FConservative-Reform coalitions.
OL,13,FTHE RESULTS
OL,15,FResults will be posted here as they
OL,16,Fcome in throughout the night.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
